{
  "stem": "18581.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 272.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the theater-- the Hebrew theater put on a performance called [NON-ENGLISH], by Pinski.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did not have the book, but the teacher Dimentman reconstructed it from memory.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I played a small part in it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- the Hebrew choir was headed by a conductor called Dumarshkin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we had sopranos, alts, tenors, and was baritones.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We sang like [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] 'Herbstlied' by Mendelssohn and song of autumn-- 'Autumn Song' by Mendelssohn.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We sang the 'Grand March' of And we song-- we sang-- we were singing also many Hebrew Zionist songs.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Once or twice a week.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It did, because I assume their line was that as long as the Judenrat exists and as long as people work and don't run away and don't go into the forests, then they should have some release, some entertainment.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was the entertainment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think that the-- the Germans knew about it as well.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was contrary to let's say the Kovno ghetto, where the leadership helped the underground.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In Vilna ghetto, I don't think it was like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were from time to time Jews killed, one or two, for various so-called offenses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But by and large it was the quiet period.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And anyway, I was concentrating on trying to get out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had a weapon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was about to go out with Dr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Leon Bernstein and his group.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in the meantime, his group fell apart.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I will not go into details.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he himself joined the FBO.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the meantime, I had to leave the ghetto quite abruptly, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because the man who sold me the weapon was caught.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was tipped off by Chaim Trapido, the director of the [NON-ENGLISH] in Vilna.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
